{"name":"Batteries.Data.Char.AsciiCasing","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Batteries.Data.Char.Basic","Batteries.Tactic.Basic","Std.Classes.Ord.String"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/a67fc66cd1ebc0855dc064a4be727798771c0f89/Batteries/Data/Char/AsciiCasing.lean#L186-L199","name":"Char.cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly","line":186,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Char/AsciiCasing.html#Char.cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly","doc":"ASCII-case insensitive implementation comparison returning an `Ordering`. Useful for sorting.\n\n```\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly 'a' 'A' -- eq\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly 'a' 'a' -- eq\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly '$' '$' -- eq\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly 'a' 'b' -- lt\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly 'γ' 'Γ' -- gt\n#eval cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly 'ä' 'Ä' -- gt\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Char/AsciiCasing.html#Char.cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly\"><span class=\"name\">Char</span>.<span class=\"name\">cmpCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">c₂</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Ord.html#Ordering\">Ordering</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/a67fc66cd1ebc0855dc064a4be727798771c0f89/Batteries/Data/Char/AsciiCasing.lean#L180-L184","name":"Char.beqCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly.isSetoid","line":180,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Char/AsciiCasing.html#Char.beqCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly.isSetoid","doc":"Setoid structure on `Char` using `beqCaseInsensitiveAsciiOnly`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=